Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:07.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,There you are, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,That's the last of your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:12.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Actually, Spike, I've got one last pile of bags, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:17.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Won't you be a dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:21.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sure… I'll be a dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:26.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,An entire week in the fabulous city of Manehattan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:29.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Plus, all of my very best friends there with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:32.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course we'd all come along to support you during Fashion Week, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Not that you'll need it. I'm sure you'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:40.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can't begin to tell you how excited I am that you'll all be there with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:44.84,Rarity,,0,0,0,,However… Perhaps I can show you…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:50.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Ooh, ooh, ooh, I know! A paper fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:51.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,No, it's…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:52.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A magic trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:57.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You know, where I pick a card and remember what it is and then you put it back in the deck so you can't look at it and…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,These are tickets to the hottest musical on Bridleway!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:04.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You couldn't mean Hinny of the Hills…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:06.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,because that show's been sold out for months!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:07.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Or could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:09.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I could. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh Rarity, you didn't have to do that, but… since you did…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:20.15,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This trip is fun already! I love jumping up and down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:12.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Come along, ponies! I found us a place to stay only a block from the train station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:15.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,in the very heart of this glorious metropolis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:23.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! That's the theatre where Hinny of the Hills is playin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:28.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wow, Rarity! How'd you manage to get us seats for tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:32.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, I gave some designs for the costume designer, so he pulled a few strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:37.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,That is what makes Manehattan so splendid and amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You do something nice for somepony,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and then you'll never know when they'll do something nice for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,So then you can do something nice for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Like get us in to see Hinny of the Hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:51.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Which is only the best musical in all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:53.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It must be good if Rainbow Dash is impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Normally she doesn't even like musicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:01.45,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ponies just bursting into song in random places at the drop of a hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:02.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Who does that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, Manehattan, what you do to me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:09.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Such a huge bustling community
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:14.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And there's always opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:17.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,To do the friendly thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:23.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If some are grouchy, pay no mind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.41,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Surprise instead with something kind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.81,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Lo and behold, you may just find
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:35.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,A smile is what you'll bring
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Mane Fair Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to take those bags to your room for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Only if you'll accept this gratuity first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.08,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho-ho! I'll get your change!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Do keep it all. I insist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:52.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Generosity, I'm here to show all that I can give
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:57.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Generosity, I'm here to set the bar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:02.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just sit back and watch how I live
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Please, take mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.25,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Wow, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Some may say, "Rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:14.61,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't be so big-hearted and bold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:18.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Treating strangers like they're friends
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:25.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This town's too big and cold"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:30.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But this is how I play my cards
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm not about to fold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:38.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Where I see a frown, I go to town
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:41.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Call me the smile patrol
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:46.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, Manehattan, what you do to us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What if you find a Gloomy Gus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's no intimidatin' thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.21,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Just be kind without a fuss
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:04.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Generosity, I'm here to show all that I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Generosity, you are the key
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:14.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Manehattan, I'm here just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:19.21,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,To think my dresses could soon be displayed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:33.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,on the most glamorous shopping thoroughfare in the most glamorous city in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, it would be my dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is there anything left to do we can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.61,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hm, not that I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The dresses are all completely finished, all made
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:46.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,from a fabulous new fabric I've been developing for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:50.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Stretchy, but not clingy. Shimmery, but not showy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.12,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Sounds amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left for me to do but check in at the runway
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:57.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,with my dresses by two this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:01.18,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's funny. Because that clock over there makes it seem like that's only ten minutes from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, my ribbons and threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And the runway ballroom is all the way across town!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If I don't get there, I'm disqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Taaaaxiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! We've gotta help her find a cab, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:19.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy! Is this cab taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:22.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The line ends back there, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:23.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Does everypony in this town want a cab?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:30.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid getting a taxi at this time could prove almost impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Please, let her have this taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She has somewhere very important to be, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:38.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not likely! She can get in line like the rest of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:43.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The cab drivers just drive right past to get to the next pony in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:51.65,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Your wheel works like a charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,So now which of you nice folks is hoppin' in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fashion runway ballroom, seven minutes. Can you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.72,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Whew, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:07.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,Anypony else got a sneaking suspicion we're forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.99,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, I'm here for Fashion Week!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.52,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Everypony's gathered in front of the runway and about to start,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:25.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,so you'll just have to bring your dresses along with you and store them backstage later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My- My dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly forget them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:32.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm dooooomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.04,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Got 'em right here, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:37.25,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Your friends told me you need these in a hurry, so I offered to race 'em over myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:39.07,Somepony,,0,0,0,,'Anything for that nice mare,' I told 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.79,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I made it! And with seconds to spare!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hello, everypony. Pleased to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.21,Prim,,0,0,0,,Rarity, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:57.31,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You must be Prim Hemline, the host of this grand event.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How do you..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:02.53,Prim,,0,0,0,,Miss Rarity, how is it that all your competitors are here half an hour early,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:05.30,Prim,,0,0,0,,and yet you arrive seconds before we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just… lucky, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:13.45,Prim,,0,0,0,,Once we're done here, you're to finish setting up backstage,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.47,Prim,,0,0,0,,so you'll be ready for your run-through appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.34,Prim,,0,0,0,,You show your designs last.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:22.95,Prim,,0,0,0,,We keep to a precise schedule, so let's try to be more than a few seconds early, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:27.33,Prim,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the contest to see which one of you gets to stay to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:29.69,Prim,,0,0,0,,top designers all across the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:32.32,Prim,,0,0,0,,The rest of you must go home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.91,Prim,,0,0,0,,So sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:35.91,Prim,,0,0,0,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.64,Prim,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you made it, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:43.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Me too, but everything just seems to keep working out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.40,Suri,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.53,Suri,,0,0,0,,Suri Polomare from the Ponyville Knitters League?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, of course, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I- I thought you looked familiar, but I couldn't place it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You haven't been back in years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:58.23,Suri,,0,0,0,,Because I moved her to make it in the big city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, good for you, Sur--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.13,Suri,,0,0,0,,Ooh, it's so good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.88,Suri,,0,0,0,,And now here, we are, competing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:11.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, well good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:12.71,Suri,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't need luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.52,Suri,,0,0,0,,Would you like a hoof with your things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:20.34,Suri,,0,0,0,,My, your collection is gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:25.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh now, I'm sure your collection is equally lovely, if not more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.69,Suri,,0,0,0,,It's alright, but nothing like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:31.31,Suri,,0,0,0,,Take my culottes for example, they are simply crying out for just the right accent,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.38,Suri,,0,0,0,,but I haven't the slightest notion where I-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:38.19,Suri,,0,0,0,,Actually… just a touch of this fabric could be perfect for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:41.63,Suri,,0,0,0,,W- Oh hey, would you mind terribly if I took a swatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all! Here, I have loads extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.40,Suri,,0,0,0,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:50.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh well, it's been wonderful getting caught up, and I don't mean to be rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but I must finish my preparations and I am a bit late as it- is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:01.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hello! I'm here half an hour early for my run-through appointment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:03.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,just the way Prim likes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Get in line over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:12.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh my, that fabric's gorgeous, did you make that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh my yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's stretchy, but not clingy. Shimmery-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.88,Suri,,0,0,0,,Shimmery, but not showy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:21.04,Suri,,0,0,0,,And the entire line is in the same adorable pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:24.02,Suri,,0,0,0,,It works on everything from the skirts to tops to shoes and,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:28.20,Prim,,0,0,0,,Oh, bravo! I've never seen anything like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:32.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You stole my fabric!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:37.53,Suri,,0,0,0,,I didn't steal it, okay? You gave it to me, 'member?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:41.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I gave you the fabric for accents! Not for your whole line!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:44.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And how could you possibly make all of those outfits out of it so fast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.44,Suri,,0,0,0,,Fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:49.12,Suri,,0,0,0,,Coco Pommel took practically forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.28,Suri,,0,0,0,,Nearly got me completely disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:54.12,Coco,,0,0,0,,Well, I wanted to make sure you'd win, so I took the extra time to--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:58.65,Suri,,0,0,0,,Quiet! I pay an assistant to sew and get coffee, not talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.07,Suri,,0,0,0,,Aw, sweetie, don't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:08.10,Suri,,0,0,0,,It takes some small-town fillies a while to learn it's everypony for herself in the big city, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:13.93,Suri,,0,0,0,,Hope you realize how fortunate you are to have me as your mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.36,Suri,,0,0,0,,Now get me some coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:21.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, what a great afternoon! It was almost too much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:25.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Better pace yourself, 'cause the rest of the day is jam-packed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:28.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,First there's the salon appointment to get our manes done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:30.32,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Then our fancy dinner at the Far-Afield Tavern!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.29,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And after that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.87,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hinny of the Hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Is… everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.28,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You got the dresses the bellhop brought you and everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:53.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But he said he brought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.84,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And then Suri stole them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:00.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I let one of the other contestants use some of my one-of-a-kind fabric
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and then she turned it into a wardrobe just like mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:06.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and only now it looks like I'm the one copying her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:10.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My generosity has ruined me, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:15.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now, Rarity, whatever went wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,we're all here to help you get through it, no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on, Rarity, buck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All we need is some fabric and you'll be back in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.61,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This new line is going to be marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Perhaps even better than the last! It's daring, it's bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:46.19,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I still have a chance after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:10.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Sew these pieces together according to that pattern there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You said if we skipped dinner at the Far-Afield Tavern
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you'd order a meal for us while we keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't fret. It'll be here in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:19.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,That's not going to be a problem, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:24.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, we're supposed to be watching Hinny of the Hills by then…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:31.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I see! I go out of my way to get you tickets for a show, and this is how you repay me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,By abandoning me in my hour of need?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:40.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fine! Go and see Hinny of the Hills tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:44.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And then tomorrow morning when you come to see my fashion show
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,without any fashion to show, you can have more entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:49.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,'Oh my, look, there's our friend Rarity going down in flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:52.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Isn't friendship magic?!'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:55.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity, calm down. What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:56.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, go ahead! Go and see your show!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Congratu-pony-lations, fillies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:06.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Seems like you've all figured out already it's everypony for herself in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:21.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There. That's the last of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:32.29,Prim,,0,0,0,,Let's have another round of applause for Suri Polomare's amazing collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:40.52,Prim,,0,0,0,,That fabric! So original!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.80,Suri,,0,0,0,,Well look who's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:48.17,Suri,,0,0,0,,Here to show off your copycat collection, mm? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:53.62,Prim,,0,0,0,,And now, Rarity from Ponyville with her brand new line
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.66,Prim,,0,0,0,,and I mean "brand new".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.59,Prim,,0,0,0,,Hotel Chic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh? They're liking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I think I may have just won this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't wait to celebrate with-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They didn't come…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.55,Prim,,0,0,0,,Rarity, they all adore you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:45.82,Prim,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to tell them about your fabulous pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.08,Prim,,0,0,0,,Come back at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.67,Prim,,0,0,0,,This is unheard of!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.62,Somepony,,0,0,0,,How'd'you do, ma'am? Contest going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:04.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,No time to talk. I have to find my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:07.36,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're gone already. I saw them headed out this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:11.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Back to Ponyville, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, they worked so hard on my behalf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:16.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And then I repaid them with unkindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:19.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.84,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But miss, I- I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:39.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, Manehattan, what have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:43.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The thought of Fashion Week was fun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:47.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But I went way too far
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:56.71,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My friends gave to me in ways so kind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:17:03.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I gave them nothing but a hard time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:07.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And now alone I stand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:12.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And now alone I stand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I need a moment with Prim Hemline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I have to rush back to Ponyville but I just wanted to thank her first for-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:27.95,Suri,,0,0,0,,you'd best steer clear of Prim for a while, she's pretty furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:28.89,Prim,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:30.66,Coco,,0,0,0,,yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,There you all are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:37.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it, I thought you went back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We missed the show because we overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Suri told us you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:44.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You know what? I don't even care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:52.86,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm just happy you're all still here after how I treated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:57.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Taking advantage of your friendship the way I did… how could you ever see past it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you were pretty rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:04.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know your thing is honesty, but come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Last night we may not have seen you at your best,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but we know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:12.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And we would never let one thing like that change how we feel about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:15.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:19.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You really are utmost wonderful friends a pony could have!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:24.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You know, I already arranged to make it up to you this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:28.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hope you're all available for an exclusive performance of Hinny of the Hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.58,Suri,,0,0,0,,And that is how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:39.58,Suri,,0,0,0,,Pretty clever how I convinced her to stay away from Prim, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:43.12,Suri,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't have wanted her to find out the truth now, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:54.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…dancing pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:05.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Wow! That was even better than I imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I loved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:13.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Uh, I mean, it was a'ight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:20.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How did you ever get them to agree to do an extra performance just for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Remember my costume designer friend who got me the tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:26.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, I offered to make all the costumes for his next show!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.91,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Um, here in Manehattan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:34.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes… it will keep me away from Ponyville for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:38.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But I still wanted you to see this show!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And working for this designer is such a great opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.31,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:44.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We're happy for you, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:46.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We're just sad for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.05,Coco,,0,0,0,,Mind if I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sure. Come on down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:59.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This is the first place trophy for Fashion Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,With my name on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But I thought I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.52,Coco,,0,0,0,,You didn't. You won.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.73,Coco,,0,0,0,,Suri was hoping that if you didn't claim your prize,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:12.60,Coco,,0,0,0,,the judges would consider it a forfeit and first place would go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:16.40,Coco,,0,0,0,,So she lied to make you and your friends go away, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.44,Coco,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:19.35,Coco,,0,0,0,,I lied too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.56,Coco,,0,0,0,,I've worked for Suri for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:25.54,Coco,,0,0,0,,I started to believe it really is everypony for herself in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:28.63,Coco,,0,0,0,,Until I saw how generous you were with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.77,Coco,,0,0,0,,And how generous they were with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.97,Coco,,0,0,0,,It made me start believing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:35.39,Coco,,0,0,0,,that there was something better for me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.83,Coco,,0,0,0,,So, I, I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:41.66,Coco,,0,0,0,,I brought you something to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:48.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I suppose you'll need a job now that you're no longer with Suri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:53.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How would you like to work for my friend making all the costumes for his next show?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Manehattan is simply grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:03.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It was in this magnificent metropolis that I learned,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:06.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,that while there are ponies that will take advantage of your generosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:10.79,Rarity,,0,0,0,,you should never ever let that cause you to abandon your generous spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:15.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Nothing feels worse than taking advantage of the giving nature of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ
